    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In honorem domus divinae <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>autae Aruranci Aramici <lb n="3"/>scholam de suo instruxerunt <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ocus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei aneinanderpassende Bruchstücke von einem Architrav; Inschriftfeld in Form einer tabula ansata. Z. 2 u. 3: hederae. (B): Schwarz; Walser, Frei-Stolba - Bielmann: Z. 2: [na]utae; Schwarz: Z. 3: [s]cholam; Z. 4: [l(ocus)].</p>
            </div>
